        By downloading, installing, accessing, or using the App, you acknowledge
        that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by the terms of
        this Agreement.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        If you do not agree to the terms of this Agreement, you must not use the
        App.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
