      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. Restrictions</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        You agree that you will not, and will not attempt to:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-700">
        <li>
          Use the App for any commercial purpose unless expressly authorized by
          Boomger.
        </li>
        <li>
          Copy, modify, decompile, reverse engineer, disassemble, or attempt to
          derive the source code of the App or any part thereof.
        </li>
        <li>Create derivative works based on the App.</li>
        <li>
          Sell, rent, lease, sublicense, distribute, or otherwise transfer the
          App to any third party.
        </li>
        <li>
          Use the App in a manner that interferes with, disrupts, damages, or
          overburdens Boomger’s systems, servers, or networks.
        </li>
        <li>
          Use the App for unlawful, harmful, abusive, or fraudulent activities,
          including misuse of the dating and community features.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Maintenance and Support</h2>
      <p>
        Boomger is solely responsible for providing any maintenance and support
