    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Warranty Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, the App is provided on an "AS
        IS" and "AS AVAILABLE" basis without warranties of any kind. Boomger
        expressly disclaims all warranties, whether express, implied, or
        statutory, including but not limited to implied warranties of
